description: The Zillow Home Value Index is the median Zestimate valuation for a given geographic area on a given day. A Zestimate is Zillow's estimate of the current market value for a home. We have tens of millions of Zestimates - one for most homes. Our data is refreshed regularly to reflect real estate transactions that could affect you - even if you're not buying or selling a house.
name: Zillow Metrics: Sale-to-List Price Ratio - Oregon
